        <h1 class="page-title">Slider</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">A Slider lets users select a numeric value (or range) by dragging a thumb along a horizontal track. It supports single-value and range selection, three sizes, optional labels, step markers, helper text, and all standard interaction states including error and disabled.</p>
        <nav class="content-tabs">
          <button class="tab-item active">Overview</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Style</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Usage</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Code</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Accessibility</button>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="main-content-area">
        <div class="main-content-inner">

        <!-- ========== OVERVIEW ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-overview">
          <h3 id="anatomy" class="doc-h3">Anatomy</h3>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">The Slider is composed of a label row, a track with active fill and draggable thumb, and optional helper/min-max labels.</p>

          <!-- Single Slider Anatomy -->
          <h4 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;">Single Slider</h4>
          <div class="anatomy-diagram" style="overflow:visible;">
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin:20px 0;padding:40px 80px;">
              <div style="position:relative;width:320px;">
                <!-- Label row -->
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px;position:relative;">
                  <div style="position:relative;">
                    <span style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text-muted);">Label</span>
                    <!-- 1 Label: marker left -->
                    <div style="position:absolute;right:calc(100% + 6px);top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">1</span><div style="width:28px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                  </div>
                  <div style="position:relative;">
                    <span style="font-size:14px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;">50</span>
                    <!-- 2 Value Badge: marker right -->
                    <div style="position:absolute;left:calc(100% + 6px);top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:row-reverse;align-items:center;gap:6px;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">2</span><div style="width:28px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Track -->
                <div style="position:relative;height:28px;display:flex;align-items:center;">
                  <div style="width:100%;height:6px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--prism-border);position:relative;">
                    <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:50%;height:100%;border-radius:3px;background:#2563eb;"></div>
                    <!-- 3 Inactive Track: marker below right half, vertical line up -->
                    <div style="position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 6px);left:75%;transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column-reverse;align-items:center;gap:4px;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">3</span><div style="width:2px;height:14px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                    <!-- 4 Active Track: marker below left half, vertical line up -->
                    <div style="position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 6px);left:25%;transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column-reverse;align-items:center;gap:4px;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">4</span><div style="width:2px;height:14px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                  </div>
                  <!-- Thumb -->
                  <div style="position:absolute;left:50%;top:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff;border:2px solid #2563eb;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);z-index:2;"></div>
                  <!-- 5 Thumb: marker above, vertical line down -->
                  <div style="position:absolute;left:50%;bottom:calc(100% + 4px);transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px;z-index:3;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">5</span><div style="width:2px;height:14px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                </div>
                <!-- Min / Max labels -->
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:14px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:16px;position:relative;">
                  <span>0</span><span>100</span>
                  <!-- 7 Min/Max Labels: marker left -->
                  <div style="position:absolute;right:calc(100% + 6px);top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">7</span><div style="width:28px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                </div>
                <!-- Helper text -->
                <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:12px;position:relative;display:inline-block;">
                  Helper text
                  <!-- 8 Helper Text: marker right -->
                  <div style="position:absolute;left:calc(100% + 6px);top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:row-reverse;align-items:center;gap:6px;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">8</span><div style="width:28px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Range Slider Anatomy -->
          <h4 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;margin-top:32px;">Range Slider</h4>
          <div class="anatomy-diagram" style="overflow:visible;">
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin:20px 0;padding:40px 80px;">
              <div style="position:relative;width:320px;">
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px;">
                  <span style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text-muted);">Label</span>
                  <span style="font-size:14px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;">20 &ndash; 80</span>
                </div>
                <div style="position:relative;height:28px;display:flex;align-items:center;">
                  <div style="width:100%;height:6px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--prism-border);position:relative;">
                    <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:20%;width:60%;height:100%;border-radius:3px;background:#2563eb;"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div style="position:absolute;left:20%;top:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff;border:2px solid #2563eb;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);z-index:2;"></div>
                  <div style="position:absolute;left:80%;top:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff;border:2px solid #2563eb;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);z-index:2;"></div>
                  <!-- 6 Focus Ring: marker above left thumb, vertical line down -->
                  <div style="position:absolute;left:20%;bottom:calc(100% + 4px);transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px;z-index:3;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">6</span><div style="width:2px;height:14px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:14px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">
                  <span>0</span><span>100</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="anat-legend" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);">
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">1</span><div><strong>Label</strong><span>Field label. Semibold 13 px. Toggleable via <code>Show Label</code>.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">2</span><div><strong>Value Badge</strong><span>Pill displaying the current value (or range). Toggleable via <code>Show Value Label</code>. Colour shifts on interaction.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">3</span><div><strong>Inactive Track</strong><span>Full-width background rail. Uses <code>Border/Border-Secondary</code>.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">4</span><div><strong>Active Track</strong><span>Filled portion indicating the selected value. Uses <code>Background/BG-Button-Primary</code>. For Range, fills between the two thumbs.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">5</span><div><strong>Thumb</strong><span>Draggable circular handle. White fill with accent border. Transforms on hover, focus, and press.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">6</span><div><strong>Focus Ring</strong><span>Outer ring visible only on keyboard focus. Uses <code>Border/Border-Accent-Focus</code>.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">7</span><div><strong>Min / Max Labels</strong><span>Optional text labels at each end of the track (hidden by default).</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">8</span><div><strong>Helper Text</strong><span>Optional contextual message below the slider (hidden by default).</span></div></div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

